frontend/src/__tests__/fixtures/avr-blink/
frontend/src/__tests__/fixtures/rp2040-blink/

# Arduino compilation byproducts in test fixtures
**/*.ino.eep
**/*.ino.with_bootloader.bin
**/*.ino.with_bootloader.hex
**/*.ino.map
**/*.ino.uf2
.claude/*
backups/*
